<cb:div type="apparatus">
<head>校勘記</head>
<p>
<choice cb:resp="#resp2" cb:from="#beg_9" cb:to="#end_9"><corr>祛</corr><sic>袪</sic></choice>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="cbeta-notes">
<head>CBETA 校勘記</head>
<p>
</p>
</cb:div>
<cb:div type="nanchuan-notes">
<head>漢譯南傳大藏經 註解</head>
<p>
<note n="0115001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0115001">三杖縛為一束具有三脚，為仙者用具之一。</note>
<note n="0115002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0115002">讀為 carā sadā（異本）。</note>
<note n="0116003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0116003">讀為 samāyutaṁ（異本）。</note>
<note n="0117004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0117004">註釋中為 Bhāgineyyupāli 與前出之優波離區別。但其內容卻與持律第一之優波離為同一人。</note>
<note n="0118001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0118001">詳解為 Soṇa-Koḷiyavessa（黃金二十億），又異本為 KotiKaṇṇa（億耳）Koḷiyavessa 或 Koḷivisa 與漢譯億耳比丘（Koṭikanna）當為另一人。可參閱 Theragāthā（南傳藏卷二五）中別出兩者之偈。漢譯則往往與此混同。此在譬喻經之各寫本中，亦同犯此類錯誤。</note>
<note n="0119002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119002">自此以下至第二十一偈止，插入有關甘蔗（okkāka.Ikṣuāku）王統之傳說。甘蔗王之子女九人為四男五女。王後立新妃，寵愛新妃及其一子，驅逐先妃之子等於國外。彼等入最上之山即雪山，住於湖畔之薩伽（Sāka）樹林中，兄妹相婚。保持血統之純潔。此即釋迦族之祖。D. 3. Ambaṭṭha（南傳藏卷六、一三七頁）、長阿卷一三、阿摩晝經 Sumangala. I. P. 174 及其他請參閱。</note>
<note n="0119003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119003">讀為 tayā。</note>
<note n="0119004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119004">甘蔗王之長女名曰 Piyā 患癩病被棄於洞窟。為拘羅（kola）市之王而出家者，於其近傍將其救出。此後裔曰拘利族。見 Cf. MahāvastuI, P. 353; Sumaṅgala, I. P. 262。</note>
<note n="0119005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119005">應視作第十三偈續述至此。予意以為甘蔗王或拘利族之祖應視為一剎帝利。</note>
<note n="0119006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0119006">Soṇa（黃金）。</note>
<note n="0120007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0120007">Aṅgīrasa（肢光）為釋尊之異名。</note>
<note n="0121001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121001">讀為 Sattukāñ Ca（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0121002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0121002">讀為 tūlikā。</note>
<note n="0123001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123001">異本中為 Santiṭṭhāpaka 或為 Sanniṭṭhāpaka。</note>
<note n="0123002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0123002">Arindama（摧敵）。</note>
<note n="0124001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0124001">Hatthiya（手）。</note>
<note n="0125001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0125001">Padumissara（蓮華自在）。</note>
<note n="0126001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0126001">或應讀為 uccatte。</note>
<note n="0126002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0126002">ratana（aratni）長度之單位，合二十一拇指中幅之長度。或與 12anguli（指）相當。</note>
<note n="0126003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0126003">hattha（hasta）譯為肘，長度之單位，為由肘至中指尖端之長度，但實測究為幾何？頗有異說。一說為一尺八寸。茲示其關係單位相互之量如次：24 anguli = 1 hasta; 4 hasta = 1 dhanu（弓）; 500 dhanu = 1 kro'sa（拘盧舍）8; kro'sa = 1 yojana（由旬）。</note>
<note n="0128001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0128001">tagara, mallikā，多羅伽略稱伽羅，為香之名。摩利迦為花之名，亦稱次第花，為一種香草。</note>
<note n="0129002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0129002">Jalajutama 即 Padumuttara 指佛而言。</note>
<note n="0129003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0129003">過去七佛之第六佛。過去二十四佛之第二十四佛。</note>
<note n="0130001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0130001">一般係指為摩訶周那，大純陀（Mahācunda）比丘。即舍利弗之弟。但在此或指為他人之混同者。</note>
<note n="0130002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0130002">Jāti 為素馨之類。</note>
<note n="0131003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131003">Dujjaya（難勝）。</note>
<note n="0131004" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131004">Vaṅganta 為舍利弗及純陀之父。</note>
<note n="0131005" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131005">Sārī（鶖鷺）。</note>
<note n="0131006" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131006">Cūḷacunda（小純陀）。</note>
<note n="0131007" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131007">兄指舍利弗（Sāriputta）。</note>
<note n="0131008" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131008">此為指舍利弗涅槃之時，彼為辦理荼毘等諸事，行施供養。此時純陀傳為舍利弗之沙彌。S. 47. 13. Cuṇḍa.（S. V. P. 161），雜阿卷二四（大正藏，卷二、一七六頁中）參閱。</note>
<note n="0131009" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0131009">讀為 dhātuṁ pattamhi ociya（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0133001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0133001">Seyya = Sayana。</note>
</p>
</cb:div>
</back></text></TEI>